    <patterns>
      <pattern name="PromptSchemaOverrideMergerTests" location="tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/PromptSchemaOverrideMergerTests.cs">
        Existing merger tests cover the merger's internal logic. This task does NOT re-test merger logic — only that the executor invokes it correctly and the merged result reaches the LLM call.
      </pattern>
      <pattern name="Moq Verify with parameter capture" location="tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Nodes/AiAnalysisNodeExecutorTests.cs">
        Use It.Is&lt;T&gt;(predicate) on _openAiClient.Setup/.Verify to capture the parameters passed to GetStructuredCompletionRawAsync and assert their merged values.
      </pattern>
    </patterns>
  </knowledge>

  <context>
    <background>
      Task 007 covered happy-path payload binding. This task adds the per-node override surface — the
      Q2 KEEP feature confirming AiCompletion preserves personalization without forcing makers to create
      a new Action for every minor variant. Tests use Moq's parameter capture to assert the merged values
      reach the LLM call.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
